Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.57,0:00:05.74,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Okay, shall we head home?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.74,0:00:06.53,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.53,0:00:07.79,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:09.01,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Look, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.01,0:00:11.80,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,It says a minstrel is coming to town!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.26,0:00:13.25,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.28,0:00:18.77,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,"The famous minstrel Schifanoia is \Npaying her first visit to Flatta."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.97,0:00:22.01,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,That's... not quite what I was expecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.28,0:00:23.83,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Anyone know who this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.83,0:00:25.99,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,I've never even heard of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.99,0:00:27.88,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,Probably some nameless chick.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.88,0:00:30.04,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,It does seem a bit sketchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.28,0:00:33.61,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Schifanoia, eh? She's certainly \Nbeen around a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.90,0:00:35.77,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You know her, Flatorte?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.03,0:00:40.42,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,I like minstrels. \NI know at least 1,000 groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.42,0:00:41.40,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,That's hardcore!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.66,0:00:45.23,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Schifanoia has only ever \Nperformed in the capital,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.23,0:00:47.69,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,but it sounds as if she's \Nbegun touring the nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.69,0:00:51.00,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,I wanna hear the minstrel sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.97,0:00:51.42,Main - Top,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Some minstrels tour all manner \Nof towns and villages,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.00,0:00:53.17,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,It might be fun to give her a listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.44,0:00:54.79,Main - Top,Flatorte,0,0,0,,while others stick to different \Nareas within the same large city
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.03,0:00:56.26,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Okay, then... since we're here...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.79,0:00:57.46,Main - Top,Flatorte,0,0,0,,and never visit towns with \Nsmall populations...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.26,0:00:57.91,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I guess we can check her out.
