Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.63,0:01:05.69,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,There are quite a lot of people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.87,0:01:07.88,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Is that Schifanoia?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:09.19,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,It appears so.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.01,0:01:25.75,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,What... is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.26,0:01:29.51,Italics - Top,Kuku,0,0,0,,Death! Death! Death! Death! Execute! \NExecute! Execute! Execute!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.31,0:01:29.21,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.21,0:01:31.09,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Let's go over there, Big Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.72,0:01:32.83,Main - Top,Villager A,0,0,0,,This is hurting my ears, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.49,0:01:34.71,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Lady Azusa, Halkara seems \Nto have a stomachache.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.83,0:01:34.40,Main - Top,Villager B,0,0,0,,Let's go home, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.40,0:01:37.34,Main - Top,Villager C,0,0,0,,I just don't get the music \Nthey like in the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.71,0:01:35.97,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,I'm going with her to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.97,0:01:37.64,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,The scale of my fake sickness is growing...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.34,0:01:39.22,Main - Top,Villager D,0,0,0,,Let's go play chess over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.12,0:01:38.87,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Hey, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.87,0:01:41.16,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,This song truly is Schifanoia's style.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.22,0:01:41.61,Main - Top,Villager E,0,0,0,,Papa, buy me some butter candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:42.52,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You know what this is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.52,0:01:45.81,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,It's death-style, from the \Ncrime-style of emotional-style.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.81,0:01:49.59,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Actually, it's a lonely-style-leaning form \Nof death-style called drag-down-style.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.59,0:01:51.56,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Sorry, I didn't understand a word of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.56,0:01:54.68,Main - Top,Kuku,0,0,0,,This is my first time coming \Nto this village on tour,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.73,0:01:54.68,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,This is the kind of stuff \Npeople in the capital like?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.68,0:01:57.27,Main - Top,Kuku,0,0,0,,but I can feel your passion!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.68,0:01:58.77,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,I think Schifanoia draws \Ncrowds of about 30 or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.27,0:02:00.58,Main - Top,Kuku,0,0,0,,This next song is another of my \Nbiggest hits, "Gray Dreams."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.77,0:02:00.30,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Less than impressive...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.86,0:02:03.62,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you knew about \Nsomeone so nameless.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.86,0:02:07.80,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Oh, it isn't about listening to famous\Nones and ignoring the nameless ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.80,0:02:10.97,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,I give all minstrels a listen \Njust because they're minstrels.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.11,0:02:14.49,Italics - Top,Kuku,0,0,0,,If you put black and white \Ntogether, you get gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.97,0:02:13.14,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Those are the words of \Nsomeone who's hooked!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.14,0:02:17.47,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Well, in crime-style, the lute tends to \Nbe given more focus than the vocals,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.94,0:02:19.01,Italics - Top,Kuku,0,0,0,,If you add even more black...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.18,0:02:17.06,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,{\a6}She's on her second song now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.68,0:02:21.21,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,but death-style has a sound that feels \Nlike it's splitting your ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.77,0:02:24.81,Italics - Top,Kuku,0,0,0,,It gets duller...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.22,0:02:28.18,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Flump.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.12,0:02:32.23,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Wait, is this part of the act?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.48,0:02:41.42,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,This is awful! \NShe's actually lost consciousness!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.42,0:02:43.20,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Yeah, I thought so!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.53,0:02:46.53,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Are you okay?! I'm gonna help you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.24,0:02:54.29,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You're awake? If anything \Nfeels off, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.25,0:02:58.08,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Grrr! Gurgle gurgle gurgle...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.34,0:02:59.30,Sign_Basic,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(192,1099)\an8\fnComic Sans MS\b1\fs50\pos(320,135)\c&H86BEF1&\3c&H525AD7&\bord4\shad0}Grrr...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.70,0:02:59.93,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:02.80,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,So good! So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.80,0:03:05.08,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,She must've been really hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:07.83,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,When you're done eating, \Nyou're welcome to take a bath, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.07,0:03:09.78,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,Okay! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.45,0:03:19.29,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,Allow me to introduce myself. \NI'm Kuku the almiraj.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.08,0:03:22.40,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,That's how you look without the makeup?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.40,0:03:24.08,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.29,0:03:26.53,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.53,0:03:30.50,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I bet you've passed out like \Nthat before, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.86,0:03:32.42,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,A few times...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:36.39,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,I can't support myself with \Nminstrel work alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.39,0:03:38.41,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,so I do some part-time jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.67,0:03:43.17,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Very few minstrels actually \Nearn enough to live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.58,0:03:47.36,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,Yes... I wanted to be like them,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:51.25,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,so I left my hometown 63 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:52.69,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,I believed that I was gonna be big...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.69,0:03:56.94,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,that I'd ditch my weak self \Nand become a great minstrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:03:59.10,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Just like a guy who left his \Nhometown to be in a band...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:02.07,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,But I couldn't get anywhere at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.41,0:04:05.34,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,Over and over, I told myself I'd quit,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.38,0:04:09.08,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,but I decided to keep trying \Njust a little longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.82,0:04:14.15,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Kuku, why don't you stay here \Nand take it easy for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.15,0:04:17.59,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,The air's fresh. It's a great \Nplace to rest and recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.91,0:04:19.95,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.42,0:04:22.36,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,But... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.04,0:04:28.50,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,I think it's time to quit music \Nand start living my second life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:30.60,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,Do you have a plan in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:35.34,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,Actually, I've gotten offers \Nfrom a few places like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:40.71,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,There's a steady demand for \Nbeastfolk in these sorts of jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:43.11,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Almiraj are particularly popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:48.18,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,I've been told numerous times that I could\Nmake all the money I need in this line of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.52,0:04:52.76,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,I thought, at this point, I should \Njust work where I'm wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:54.62,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,So, Kuku...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:04:57.19,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Do you not like music anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.93,0:04:59.34,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.68,0:05:02.26,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,I love music!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.86,0:05:07.43,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Really? You shouldn't quit \Nmaking music, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:08.40,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Stick with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.61,0:05:09.26,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.26,0:05:11.55,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You might not be making any money now,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:17.09,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,but you never would've kept it up \Nthis long if you didn't love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.09,0:05:19.31,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,It'd be a shame to just give that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.58,0:05:22.02,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I bet you'd regret it one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.97,0:05:27.12,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,If you're optimistic about starting \Na new job, I won't stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.44,0:05:29.78,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,But that's not what you're doing right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.78,0:05:32.62,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,so you should stick with what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.11,0:05:35.47,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,For now, just devote yourself to your music
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.47,0:05:38.08,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,while you think about your \Nfuture one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:40.29,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You can stay here in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.29,0:05:42.64,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,B-But I can't pay rent...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.64,0:05:44.01,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You don't need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:46.41,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I'm the one who told you \Nto stick with music,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.41,0:05:48.35,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,so I'll do everything I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:51.68,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,I appreciate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.02,0:05:56.22,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,To celebrate our new friendship, \Nlet me play for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:06:02.39,Main - Top,Kuku,0,0,0,,Welcome to my feast of \Ndeath and destruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.52,0:06:02.79,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,Her personality changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.79,0:06:06.27,Italics - Top,Kuku,0,0,0,,Poison, poison, poison, poison, \Npoison, poison, poison...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.27,0:06:09.53,Italics - Top,Kuku,0,0,0,,Wormwood... Wormwood...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.45,0:06:11.43,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,I can't tell how it's any different \Nfrom her other songs!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.08,0:06:13.58,Italics - Top,Kuku,0,0,0,,Poison, poison, poison, poison, \Npoison, poison, poison...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:13.39,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,They all sound the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:15.74,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,That's a pretty real complaint!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.58,0:06:17.31,Italics - Top,Kuku,0,0,0,,Wormwood... Wormwood...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:18.64,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Sorry, Kuku, but could you stop now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:22.48,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,Wh-Who are you talking to?! \NI am Schifanoia!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.48,0:06:24.15,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,I'm here to bring true despair to all of—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:25.35,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You can drop that act.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.90,0:06:28.10,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,I messed up in two spots...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:31.01,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,I couldn't give you a good performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.01,0:06:33.50,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I think we're way beyond that level here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.80,0:06:36.10,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Speaking from the perspective \Nof a listener,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.10,0:06:39.03,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,lonely-style-leaning death-style \Ndoesn't sell in this day and age.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.03,0:06:42.70,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Why don't you try some \Nflowery-style-leaning excessive-style?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.70,0:06:47.96,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,Yes, but... I really prefer the death-style \Nthat lets me use my artistry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:51.62,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,I bet you're just afraid to \Ndo something that sells.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.62,0:06:52.95,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,Th-That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.95,0:06:53.85,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,It is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:58.66,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,You do tend to look down on minstrels \Nwho have a lot of fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.66,0:07:00.33,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,Is this a drinking party \Nfor young band boys?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:04.17,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,And forget using your artistry. \NYou just suck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:06.92,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,I-I'm doing the best I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.14,0:07:09.18,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,Amateurs should just stay out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.18,0:07:12.40,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Oh? Let me see your lute, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:13.89,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,It's not a guitar?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.88,0:07:26.50,Italics,Flatorte,0,0,0,,The clear, sunny sky just makes \Nthis Sabbath even colder
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.94,0:07:33.79,Italics,Flatorte,0,0,0,,I yawn as I wait for you to arrive
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.15,0:07:42.56,Italics,Flatorte,0,0,0,,To a place higher than the clouds, \Nwhere there's no background noise
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:47.53,Italics,Flatorte,0,0,0,,We'll fly, let's fly
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.33,0:07:52.30,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,That's amazing, Flatorte! I didn't \Nknow you had that kind of talent!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.99,0:07:58.70,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,You see? Even an amateur like the \Ngreat Flatorte can manage that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:02.08,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,If you understand, \Nthen stop making excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.23,0:08:04.85,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.85,0:08:06.59,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Gloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:08.00,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Hey, you know, I was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:10.87,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Why don't you try writing lyrics \Nthat are easier to understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.87,0:08:14.55,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,But I've been performing \Nthis way for so long now,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:16.88,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,I wouldn't know what's \Neasy to understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.81,0:08:19.61,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Blink, blink!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.85,0:08:22.04,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Since we have such a big family,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.04,0:08:24.59,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,let's have everyone write some lyrics!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.05,0:08:28.14,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll start with Laika.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.22,0:08:32.01,sign_12182_176_Ah__Devotion,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,726)}Ah, Devotion
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.22,0:08:32.01,sign_12182_176_Ah__Devotion,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,726)\fs22\an4\pos(62,298)}Laika   Lyrics \N\NKuku   Music
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.51,0:08:43.04,Italics,Laika,0,0,0,,Only through step-by-step devotion
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:46.54,Italics,Laika,0,0,0,,Can one achieve anything
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:48.33,Italics,Laika,0,0,0,,And—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.87,0:08:53.10,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I think the message is a little \Ntoo direct for song lyrics.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.10,0:08:54.63,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Unusable. Try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:55.69,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,D'oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.02,0:08:57.79,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Okay, next is Halkara.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.90,0:09:03.28,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,My lyrics are great! They'd sell for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.28,0:09:03.96,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Jingle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.96,0:09:06.96,Sign_Basic,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,724)\an8\fnArial\b1\fs34\3c&HA45D68&\shad0\bord1.5\pos(320,45)}Halkara Pharmaceuticals'
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.96,0:09:06.96,Sign_Basic,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,724)\an2\fnArial\b1\fs34\3c&HA45D68&\shad0\bord1.5\pos(320,295)}Nutri-Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.96,0:09:06.96,sign_12182_176_Ah__Devotion,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,724)\fs22\an4\pos(45,296)}Halkara   Lyrics\N\NKuku       Music
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:11.96,Italics,Halkara,0,0,0,,One more push to get through work today!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.93,0:09:14.04,Italics,Halkara,0,0,0,,Nu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.22,0:09:14.34,sign_12182_176_Ah__Devotion,Text,0,0,0,,{\q2\3c&H000000&}~Performance Halted~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.35,0:09:16.05,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Okay, next!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.05,0:09:19.63,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Master! At least give me \Nconstructive criticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.64,0:09:21.64,sign_12182_176_Ah__Devotion,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,724)\bord1.5}The Field
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.64,0:09:21.64,sign_12182_176_Ah__Devotion,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,724)\fs22\an4\bord1.5\pos(34,307)}Falfa & Shalsha   Lyrics\N\NKuku                     Music
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.39,0:09:29.25,Italics,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Praying mantises are scary
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:33.71,Italics,Shalsha,0,0,0,,They're scary because \Nthey have those scythes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.71,0:09:37.83,Italics,Falfa,0,0,0,,Grasshoppers jump
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.83,0:09:42.40,Italics,Falfa,0,0,0,,They shake their legs to jump
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.40,0:09:46.28,Italics,Falfa,0,0,0,,Nature is so big
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.28,0:09:50.43,Italics,Shalsha,0,0,0,,And I am part of nature, too
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.43,0:09:54.42,Italics,Falfa,0,0,0,,What am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.42,0:09:58.79,Italics,Shalsha,0,0,0,,I am a being that amounts to nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.79,0:10:06.49,Italics,Both,0,0,0,,In other words, I think that means I'm me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.03,0:10:15.33,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I love it! So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.33,0:10:18.99,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Yes... Its theological elements \Nmight be rather novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.99,0:10:20.19,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.42,0:10:22.02,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,And last is Rosalie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.02,0:10:23.46,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.96,0:10:29.96,sign_12182_176_Ah__Devotion,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,766)}Nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.96,0:10:29.96,sign_12182_176_Ah__Devotion,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,766)\fs22\an4\bord1.5\pos(45,300)}Rosalie   Lyrics\N\NKuku     Music
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.21,0:10:33.94,Italics,Rosalie,0,0,0,,When you've been stuck in \None place for a long time
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.02,0:10:38.79,Italics,Rosalie,0,0,0,,Even the daytime seems dark
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:45.43,Italics,Rosalie,0,0,0,,So dark, so dark, so dark, \Nthere's truly nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.74,0:10:50.08,Italics,Rosalie,0,0,0,,I don't even know how to laugh anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:57.94,Italics,Rosalie,0,0,0,,Even though I want to die, I can't
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.92,0:11:03.52,Italics,Rosalie,0,0,0,,That's what that night was like
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.11,0:11:08.42,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Gloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:11.49,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm having fun now, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.84,0:11:16.61,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,I was singing about things \Nlike destruction and death,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:19.56,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,but it was all just words. \NI've never actually died.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.56,0:11:20.55,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,No kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.55,0:11:24.39,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,So... I realize now that I can't beat \Nthe power of words spoken in truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.42,0:11:27.15,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Sparkle, sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.69,0:11:31.43,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,I'm going to abandon the name Schifanoia \Nand go by my real name, Kuku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.69,0:11:37.23,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,And I'm going to try writing a new song \Nincorporating all of your lyrics!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.22,0:12:11.72,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,Thank you all so much for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.92,0:12:16.18,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,If you're ever in the area on tour, \Ndrop by the highlands to see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.18,0:12:19.49,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,In fact, you can think \Nof it as coming home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.49,0:12:21.38,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,I will! I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.41,0:12:24.45,Main,Flartorte,0,0,0,,Put on good concerts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.45,0:12:26.66,Main,Flartorte,0,0,0,,If you can do that, \Neverything will work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.47,0:12:28.15,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.15,0:12:31.25,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Frankly, you have no musical talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:35.71,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,But success in this world doesn't \Nalways favor the talented first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.71,0:12:39.01,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,So it's possible that even you \Ncould end up successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.39,0:12:43.84,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,First, you have to fight! \NThen just keep fighting from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:44.91,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:48.08,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,They're master and pupil already.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.56,0:12:53.11,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,I got some great sake, \Nso I brought it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.11,0:12:56.51,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Beelzebub, welcome! \NYou don't have work to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.27,0:12:57.71,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Spinny spin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.51,0:12:58.31,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,It's my day off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:01.84,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,I'm spending today with Falfa and Shalsha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.74,0:13:04.48,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.48,0:13:06.71,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,I'm Kuku the minstrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.71,0:13:09.26,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,She's been staying here at \Nthe house for reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:10.12,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.30,0:13:12.99,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Then you should sing while we drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.99,0:13:16.25,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Hey, don't put her on the spot like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.25,0:13:18.04,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:20.13,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,No, please let me do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.68,0:13:24.04,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,To find out if I can get by \Nas my new, reborn self...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.90,0:13:29.47,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,I want someone who doesn't know me \Nto hear my song and be the judge!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.09,0:13:37.48,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,Thank you for listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.57,0:13:43.27,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.60,0:13:45.25,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,That was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.44,0:13:47.56,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:50.85,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,I want you to perform at \Nour next music festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:51.99,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.19,0:13:56.27,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,It's the biggest demon music event \Nheld in the castle town of Vanzeld.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:13:57.76,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,So it's a festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.76,0:14:00.50,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,I'll invite all of you, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:01.65,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:03.89,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Kuku, was it? Will you perform for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.89,0:14:05.95,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,Yes, if you'll have me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.95,0:14:09.06,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,Oh, but how big is the stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.06,0:14:13.45,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Well, you'll be performing for \Nan audience of about 20,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.45,0:14:14.81,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,Twenty thousand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.32,0:14:17.90,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Kuku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.90,0:14:21.04,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,Um... I'll practice like \Nmy life depends on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.31,0:14:24.50,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,so would you mind letting \Nme stay here a bit longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.91,0:14:28.52,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,It looks like our life with \NKuku isn't over just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.20,0:14:34.21,Eyecatch,Title,0,0,0,,{\pos(120,335)}I've Been Killing {\c&HE4AE06&}Slimes\N{\c&H313536&}for {\c&HE4AE06&}300 Years {\c&H313536&}and\N{\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H7600D0&}Maxed Out {\c&H313536&\3c&HFFFFFF&}My {\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H7600D0&}Level
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.10,0:14:38.75,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,Now, everyone, \Nplease enjoy our music festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:40.21,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Thanks, Fatla.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:45.05,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,You're welcome to visit the stage and \Nrehearse before the event tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.05,0:14:46.22,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,Would you like to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.37,0:14:47.91,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.91,0:14:50.56,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,It's a much bigger stage \Nthan any I've experienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.38,0:14:53.72,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Kuku, give it your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.72,0:14:54.80,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.80,0:14:57.85,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Master, what shall we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.85,0:14:59.85,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,There are a bunch of shops set up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.10,0:15:02.01,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,I want to go see!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.01,0:15:03.11,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.77,0:15:16.92,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,That was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.38,0:15:25.28,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Kuku, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:28.82,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,I visited the venue, \Nand it was just too big.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:31.76,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,When I think of performing on that stage...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:34.29,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,The new Kuku will pull through just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.29,0:15:39.18,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,That's right. I'm no expert, but I can \Nstill tell that you've improved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.51,0:15:41.53,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,I hope so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.53,0:15:42.98,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,You'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.31,0:15:47.13,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,You already have the perseverance to stick \Nwith the same thing for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:50.03,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,You were just investing your \Neffort in the wrong way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:53.95,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Now that you've fixed that, you can \Nput on a good performance for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.04,0:15:56.08,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.08,0:16:01.71,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,For all you say, Flatorte, you have no \Nperseverance and never invest effort for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.71,0:16:04.47,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Wh-Wh-Wh-Wh-Wh-What do you mean by that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.63,0:16:09.40,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Well, you only crashed my sister \NLeila's wedding on a whim, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:11.58,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,If you wanted to defeat us Red Dragons,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.58,0:16:14.21,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,shouldn't you have started trying sooner?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.21,0:16:17.46,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,That was the kind of thing \Nthat's best done on a whim!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.01,0:16:21.90,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Well, even if you had tried, \NI doubt you could have beaten us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:24.46,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Fine! Let's settle this right here and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.46,0:16:26.62,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Okay, you two, that's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.86,0:16:30.12,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,We'll have a contest to see who has \Nbetter luck in today's horoscope.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.12,0:16:31.36,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,I accept!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.36,0:16:33.36,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,That's {\i1}too{\i0} peaceful a solution!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.17,0:16:37.17,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,What are you laughing at?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.17,0:16:40.05,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,I'm sorry... I didn't mean to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.64,0:16:46.53,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Kuku, you've done all you could.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.53,0:16:50.46,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,All that's left is to let the \Naudience hear your song!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:52.03,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.04,0:17:01.09,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,How's Kuku doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.43,0:17:04.85,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,She was a little nervous, \Nbut I think she's okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.11,0:17:09.37,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Beelzebub, thanks for offering \NKuku this opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.52,0:17:13.07,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,All I did was give her a opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:18.54,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Whether or not she seizes \Nthat opportunity is up to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:31.21,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,I'm Kuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.60,0:17:33.79,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,The song I'm about to perform...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:41.79,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,is called "Thank You."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.00,0:18:10.09,Italics,Kuku,0,0,0,,I know that
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.09,0:18:15.47,Italics,Kuku,0,0,0,,I should be saying goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.47,0:18:20.39,Italics,Kuku,0,0,0,,But that would be too sad
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.22,0:18:24.89,Italics,Kuku,0,0,0,,So I'll say this instead
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.23,0:18:28.23,Italics,Kuku,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.23,0:18:33.99,Italics,Kuku,0,0,0,,I'm not disappearing and going away forever
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.99,0:18:42.20,Italics,Kuku,0,0,0,,We'll both still be living under the same sky
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:49.75,Italics,Kuku,0,0,0,,In different places, but at the same time
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.75,0:18:57.64,Italics,Kuku,0,0,0,,There may be things that we forget
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.64,0:19:01.35,Italics,Kuku,0,0,0,,Because we are alive
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.35,0:19:09.11,Italics,Kuku,0,0,0,,But because we're alive, we can remember
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.11,0:19:12.23,Italics,Kuku,0,0,0,,Yes, we can remember
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:17.74,Italics,Kuku,0,0,0,,So whenever you feel like it, at least,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.95,0:19:22.83,Italics,Kuku,0,0,0,,Come and see me, please come and see me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.83,0:19:27.92,Italics,Kuku,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.12,0:19:33.50,Italics,Kuku,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.63,0:19:40.51,Italics,Kuku,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.94,0:20:12.29,Main,All,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.48,0:20:14.51,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Kuku, you were awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.51,0:20:16.99,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,I never thought it would go so well!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.99,0:20:19.05,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,I owe everything to all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.30,0:20:21.25,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,I don't know how to thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:22.06,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.37,0:20:24.97,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,There's only one thing to \Nsay at a time like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:27.03,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,"Thank you," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.36,0:20:29.19,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.80,0:20:33.81,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,You've already got a ton of requests from \Nthe organizers to make appearances!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.69,0:20:35.77,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.95,0:20:39.90,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,It looks like enough work to keep me \Ngoing in the capital for a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.90,0:20:41.40,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Good for you, Kuku!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.40,0:20:43.57,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You've become an overnight sensation!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.57,0:20:44.56,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.29,0:20:51.58,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Kuku, can I borrow your lute?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.63,0:20:55.09,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.79,0:20:59.36,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,I have a song for you. \NIt's not a very good one, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.61,0:21:09.81,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.81,0:21:11.86,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Schifanoia!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.78,0:21:16.96,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,As Schifanoia, you sang so hard \Nthat you lost consciousness!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:19.56,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Of course you wouldn't get popular \Nwith music like this, but still!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.83,0:21:22.58,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,You kept doing it because \Nyou believed it was right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.58,0:21:25.03,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,So if you ever want to go back, you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.49,0:21:29.33,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Don't you dare get any dumb ideas \Nabout giving up on it forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:33.31,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,You're not clever enough to keep up \Nwith what's popular in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.31,0:21:35.83,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,If you were, you would've \Nbeen popular long ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.83,0:21:40.38,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Even I, Flatorte, got it wrong \Nover and over and over again...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.59,0:21:46.31,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,And now, I'm living here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.31,0:21:49.33,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,There is no right answer, but as \Nlong as you don't stop completely,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.33,0:21:51.31,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,there are no total failures!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.60,0:21:54.97,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,So you just sing however you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.73,0:21:58.08,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,That's what your life is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.07,0:22:03.91,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.91,0:22:06.19,Main,Kuku,0,0,0,,I'll do my best right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.97,0:22:10.12,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,They're definitely master and pupil.
